" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fd573e66-96a1-475f-a1b0-c208361bb574\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-82d3f0ac-c5f0-4fe0-aaaa-99691bb75afc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ddf44382-d5eb-4339-90d1-a51a9ad31fdb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">포스터의 인쇄는 단면인쇄가 기본입니다. 다만 요즘은 배면인쇄로 양쪽 유리를 통해 알릴 수 있도록 양면인쇄를 하는경우도 많습니다. 양면인쇄인 경우는 별도의 문의를 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-587af309-47e0-4dee-834b-84f4e0f099d6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b2ec0fa5-7fca-49ff-8ce5-01496c6b150d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc8f9a09-2227-4512-b677-b32f15ddb9ff\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b9465630-4542-4434-bfc7-36621c3e1882\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-37fe841b-e268-4aa4-81d6-b3637ae0ceb4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-34e6b3d9-947f-4ed2-9ff5-997c1d611faf\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjZfMjA2/MDAxNjY5NDM2NTkyNTAy.wWuJTKaSqDE3zvnUrmJJ-RB8IkfdyuoOxnZ2BdUfy-kg.qu4CqcdNYUHEYwmpvPqOJTIo0R1AJVZAPxr_qF8Oiwkg.PNG.cookthedesign/s3.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"660\", \"originalHeight\" : \"238\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMjZfMjA2/MDAxNjY5NDM2NTkyNTAy.wWuJTKaSqDE3zvnUrmJJ-RB8IkfdyuoOxnZ2BdUfy-kg.qu4CqcdNYUHEYwmpvPqOJTIo0R1AJVZAPxr_qF8Oiwkg.PNG.cookthedesign/s3.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6810f41c-61d4-4b9d-b693-1e2317a495e8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dd37f9d6-a06f-40f1-9917-ec8563093b2b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>후가공</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a938f30-0b7d-4697-998c-69ff12297302\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6990c396-85b2-4213-afb2-ab29640f1139\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">포스터의 후가공은 한쪽면 코팅입니다. 코팅처리는 인쇄물의 보호 및 파손을 대비하며 조금 더 오랜기간 햇빛이나 노출을 보호하는 역할을 합니다. 거의 유광/무광의 단면 코팅을 하여 인쇄물을 보호하는 작업을 많이 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-10e8e86f-29d2-4747-bffa-76f4094bd5b5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3a8297ec-2979-422b-83f9-008d74657ae4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0534394a-d473-44a4-85d7-e488e0127205\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3bbecf3e-8e52-4479-8bf6-2a67e50b0b19\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</d